{"tid":2394192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立即煞停 封區禁足","createTime":"2021-02-04T04:18:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T04:54:00.000Z","uid":261647,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0f1b146c4b95997182e60c8c45d25e55ede94b9d","tid":2394192,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:18:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nostakemedicalstudent/posts/244448710571654\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnostakemedicalstudent%2Fposts%2F244448710571654&d=LTOHNK%2B9fuVs8qin7tjZRCukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=1daac51d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nostakemedicalstudent/posts/244448710571654</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NFgm1tM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNFgm1tM.jpg&h=9d98aa84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：No Stake 醫學生<br />\n<br />\n【 立即煞停 封區禁足 】<br />\n<br />\n如果當年我地覺得轉「反送中」ProPic、校友聯署\u001d唔會有用所以唔做，就唔會有香港人嘅2019。<br />\n<br />\n過去幾日，北角、藍田、元朗、尖沙咀、九龍城、油麻地，到處都有人帶同武器四出堵路，揚言要「突襲式遍地開花」，到處圍困香港巿民，阻住巿民返工放工、出街買外賣，破壞香港人嘅安居樂業。<br />\n<br />\n所謂抗疫政策，擾民就擾左，一宗確診都搵唔到。<br />\n<br />\n我當然知呢個政府唔聽民意，但即使如此，我地都要做好自己本份，先可以鬧佢唔聽。呢個時候，六區連續失敗，我地要做嘅本份，就係凝聚清晰嘅民意訴求，要求政府停止荒謬絕倫嘅封區禁足。<br />\n<br />\n或者有人會覺得，仲覺得咁樣係網絡嗌下就可以改變到政府啲咩，係死蠢死左膠；而我其實都有少少覺。但係係咩無用㗎啦，但始終唔可以未做就話冇用。應做嘅，總係要做嘅。時代黑暗，更要堅毅耕種。<br />\n<br />\n如果你都唔認同呢個突襲封區，今日，請同我一齊，用各種渠道平台，要求<br />\n<br />\n「立即煞停 封區禁足"},{"pid":"500b6d09c5b499d1abb645dcd59baeae1a26d870","tid":2394192,"uid":228955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:25:03.000Z","msg":"唔同意喎攬炒之母繼續攬炒繼續封區冇人出街冇人做生意太好了"},{"pid":"3320e4fe8c65cb171885e90725220f94e52b7968","tid":2394192,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:25:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4349238e66a7273a8989ddd50568c519be9d444","tid":2394192,"uid":250654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:30:10.000Z","msg":"封區檢測愚蠢至極注定失敗<br />\n成事不足敗事有餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人民銳評：「封區檢測」是香港經濟文明之恥<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2394189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2394189</a>"},{"pid":"dfd94c643719af52c0e6807f0d83d422604f7957","tid":2394192,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:31:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b98971cdcb4bf044958ca9ed5392bb1206d0f312","tid":2394192,"uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:33:50.000Z","msg":"香港人每晚睇人仆街睇到好開心<br />\n睇封區直播好睇過睇綜藝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7125bfc068674dedb230293966df17bcf67d03c","tid":2394192,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:36:44.000Z","msg":"19年就睇人直播示威食花生，21年就睇人直播政府封區食生花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港 移民！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f361af2354924405a705c217dc484de1fb25b8bc","tid":2394192,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b98971cdcb4bf044958ca9ed5392bb1206d0f312","tid":2394192,"uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:33:50.000Z","msg":"香港人每晚睇人仆街睇到好開心<br />\n睇封區直播好睇過睇綜藝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:45:10.000Z","msg":"撐政府抗疫 網民齊聲贊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d651962a9a443eb4997cde6c72f5b0c674df6b2a","tid":2394192,"uid":320902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T04:54:00.000Z","msg":"繼續屌正苦"}]}